Status: Backend functional, frontend styling/UX incomplete
SETUP & ACCESS
1. Repository Access

bash
# Clone repository (if not already done)
git clone <repository-url>
cd WS2025-SE-Bellis-ev

# Create Python virtual environment
python3 -m venv venv
source venv/bin/activate  # Linux/Mac
# OR
venv\Scripts\activate  # Windows

# Install dependencies
pip install -r requirements.txt

2. Database Setup

bash
cd src

# Run migrations
python manage.py migrate

# Load test data (users + reference data)
python manage.py loaddata fixtures/seed_data.json

Test Users Created:

    user_basis / test123 (BASIS role - basic permissions)

    user_erweitert / test123 (ERWEITERT - can delete, manage reference data)

    user_admin / test123 (ADMIN - full access)

3. Start Development Server

bash
# From src/ directory
python manage.py runserver

# Server runs at: http://127.0.0.1:8000/
# Or specify port: python manage.py runserver 8001

4. Access Application

    Main App: http://localhost:8000/cases/

    Login Page: http://localhost:8000/login/

    Admin Interface: http://localhost:8000/admin/


