        "Neue Beratung" button
        Edit/Delete actions per session
    Section 4: Gewalttaten list (table with dates, types, perpetrator count)
        "Neue Gewalttat" button
        Edit/Delete actions per incident

    Action Buttons (top-right):
        "Bearbeiten" (Edit) - all users
        "Abschließen" (Close) - if not closed
        "Löschen" (Delete) - only ERWEITERT/ADMIN
        Permission-based visibility

Testing:
