    Validation errors display inline (red text below field)
    Form-level errors display at top
    Conditional fields hidden/shown based on logic (JavaScript):
        informationsquelle="andere Quelle" → show informationsquelle_andere_details
        schwerbehinderung="JA" → show grad_der_behinderung + form_der_behinderung


